data.description: Live on nature's edge within Reeths Puffer School district! This 4-bed, 3-bath home on 1.1 acres offers an abundance of space for both relaxation and entertainment. With multiple gathering areas, generously sized bedrooms, and the luxury of three full baths, this home caters to both comfort and convenience. Tucked away on a private street, yet just moments from the excitement of Lake Michigan's white sand beaches, Michigan Adventure, winter sports activities, hiking trails, and opportunities to immerse yourself in nature, it's the perfect blend of tranquility and adventure. Complete with a 2-stall garage and a storage shed, this home epitomizes the ideal Michigan lifestyle! HOA fees are under $200 and cover snow removal. Buyers and Buyer agents are to verify all information.
